information: R.S. Agrotècnica del Segrià was founded in 2003. Since then it has continued its long tradition of exporting olive trees (Olea Europa). Always offering quality products. We have a nursery offering 6, 000 different trees of all sizes and prices. The smallest trees we sell have a circumference of 15-20 cm, and the largest are 240-280 cm.
